{"tid":1811683,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"PaulPogba：中國正在用youtube廣告「審查」全世界youtuber既言論","createTime":"2020-01-05T01:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T02:10:04.000Z","uid":251052,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"81c5982b4e9acbd7f91fe096ca3b8f016d1e415a","tid":1811683,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T01:50:49.000Z","msg":"你地有冇留意到YouTube越黎越多支那手遊約炮app既廣告？<br />\n根據我個人非正式統計，依家youtube有7-8成既廣告客戶都係來自中國，仲要唔止香港有呢種情況，連台灣日韓 歐洲都係，而好似華為呢d國家級財團更加係落重本係歐洲賣廣告<br />\n<br />\n可能有人會問 落廣告又點控制你言論自由呀？<br />\n我想講 youtube既廣告營利機制同演算法係好複雜 我係呢度唔能夠解釋清楚 但有一樣嘢好關鍵&mdash;&mdash;「黃標」<br />\n根據 YouTube 官方說法，如果影片<span style=\"color: red;\">「不適合多數廣告客戶」</span>，那麼該內容旁邊的營利圖示（美元符號），就會從「綠色」轉成「黃色」，這即是俗稱的「黃標」。<br />\n而被「黃標」既影片係無法盈利同較難推薦比更多用戶觀看。<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有冇追開台灣youtuber，追開既應該會感覺到臨近台灣總統大選呢段時間，越黎越多youtuber出聲抱怨youtube又黃標咗佢條片<br />\n<br />\n所以，中國可能正利用緊youtube廣告「審查」全世界youtuber既言論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a098d0c56c49622b3d97d82d40089e15b15fe4c2","tid":1811683,"uid":145277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T01:57:00.000Z","msg":"thanks for ur info"},{"pid":"deefa7618ce30412d0e2989ac9e7dac11fd41ab0","tid":1811683,"uid":50361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T01:58:00.000Z","msg":"唔明喎"},{"pid":"a81371a62ab6f4b4b5434004bacd812bb8278675","tid":1811683,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T01:59:43.000Z","msg":"咁中國公司鍾意落啲廣告去乜嘢類型嘅影片，係佢哋自由；正如我哋鍾意去黃店食嘢，都係我哋嘅自由，其他人冇權過問"},{"pid":"8dbc0bb6fd4325ee8d3ca0e47af117ce9d439d09","tid":1811683,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"deefa7618ce30412d0e2989ac9e7dac11fd41ab0","tid":1811683,"uid":50361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T01:58:00.000Z","msg":"唔明喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T02:02:52.000Z","msg":"例如支那廣告商 可以投訴某反共頻道既影片唔適合佢既廣告 <br />\nyoutube就會「黃標」該反共頻道既片"},{"pid":"2d6eb7f99d703d68e8eb74e397836a1c6b8fbde6","tid":1811683,"uid":25066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T02:04:38.000Z","msg":"即係變相控制言論自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e77149dd888ceada04a6a4388a7aeb777f4f64","tid":1811683,"uid":41906,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T02:04:55.000Z","msg":"你自己on99睇得多中國野先出得多中國廣告<br />\n我住東京又唔見我打開youtube會見到中國廣告<br />\n一係就grammer廣告一係就國內廣告"},{"pid":"00e3bcc4ef87cd851ef5df2e1cac381a056006f3","tid":1811683,"uid":251052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a81371a62ab6f4b4b5434004bacd812bb8278675","tid":1811683,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T01:59:43.000Z","msg":"咁中國公司鍾意落啲廣告去乜嘢類型嘅影片，係佢哋自由；正如我哋鍾意去黃店食嘢，都係我哋嘅自由，其他人冇權過問"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T02:05:17.000Z","msg":"中國人擅長利用西方國家既自由民主去反自由民主小粉紅例子太多 <br />\n呢個係民主自由既漏洞"},{"pid":"12e110e627bec3edbfc57485dad5b749f1d3a2d2","tid":1811683,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T02:06:26.000Z","msg":"個黃標一般人睇唔到？"},{"pid":"8d3c58003d8595f7c1d7a209d474a7ec4bc3bf86","tid":1811683,"uid":28068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T02:07:22.000Z","msg":"一日到黑都etoro同grammarly廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e895958c03788a8f92a011aa493f7f210e474b4","tid":1811683,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12e110e627bec3edbfc57485dad5b749f1d3a2d2","tid":1811683,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T02:06:26.000Z","msg":"個黃標一般人睇唔到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T02:07:28.000Z","msg":"只有影片上傳者自己睇到"},{"pid":"caa352b9dd4a732fde54d180debdd9f11566ace5","tid":1811683,"uid":201214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2e77149dd888ceada04a6a4388a7aeb777f4f64","tid":1811683,"uid":41906,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T02:04:55.000Z","msg":"你自己on99睇得多中國野先